## `@hero`
@divider

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| type | block directive |
| path | `directives/builtins.js` |
| description | prominent `<section>` wrapper, modifiers are mapped to CSS classes |
| `.center` | center-align content |
@row
@card .secondary
##* Usage

```mq
@hero .center
# Big statement!!!
A short supporting line.
@end hero
```
