@card .primary
## `@product-card`
@divider

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| type | block directive |
| path | `directives/product-card.js` |
| description | renders a `<product-card>` custom element |
| `.featured` | applies featured border styling via the `variant` attribute |
| `label` | becomes the `title` attribute on the element |

@row
@card .secondary
##* Usage

```mq
@product-card .featured Starter
## Fast setup
Copy the starter and change the theme later.
@end product-card
```
@end card
@card .tertiary
##* Preview

@product-card .featured Starter
##* Fast setup
Copy the starter and change the theme later.
@end product-card
@end card
@end row
@end card

