@card .primary
## `@row`
@divider

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| type | block directive |
| path | `directives/builtins.js` |
| description | responsive grid whose columns are sized by the number of block directive children |
| note | warns at build time if it has no block directive children |

@row
@card .secondary
##* Usage

```mq
@row
  @card
    🡸 I'm on the left!
  @end card
  @card .right
    I'm on the right. 🡺
  @end card
@end row
```
@end card


@card .tertiary
##* Preview


@row
  @card
    🡸 I'm on the left!
  @end card
  @card .right
    I'm on the right. 🡺
  @end card
@end row

_Politics in a nutshell_
@callout .warn
The content in a row is responsive, so on smaller screen the columns may stack vertically instead of horizontally.
@end callout

@end card

@end row
@end card



