## `@stat`
@divider

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| type | block directive |
| path | `directives/builtins.js` |
| description | value and label pair, extracted from the first `##` and `p` in the rendered children |

@row
@card .secondary
##* Usage

```mq
